{"tid":936960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞士修法通過，「恐同」行為將面臨三年監禁","createTime":"2018-12-11T07:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T14:31:40.000Z","uid":54870,"like":27,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a45e02aa6be9b86bd47f1dfc079ca751cd8d8079","tid":936960,"uid":54870,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"《法新社》報導，和法國、奧地利、荷蘭與丹麥一樣，瑞士也將動用《刑法》來制裁歧視同性戀的行為。瑞士下議院在今年9月25日，以118票贊成、60票反對、5票棄權，通過修法，送交聯邦院（Council of States）審議，聯邦院也在12月3日通過該修正法案，未來將擴大《刑法》第261條的反歧視範圍，將等同種族歧視的行為，一同制裁針對「性傾向」的歧視。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，未來如果有人公開宣稱：「所有同性戀者都應該被拉到集中營關起來」，將可以被追究法律責任，因為恐同產生的暴力行為，也可依法進行登記。而這些因為「性傾向」產生的歧視和仇恨言論，將比照因種族、族裔、宗教信仰產生歧視的行為，一併被視為刑事犯罪，最高可判處3年的監禁或罰款。<br />\n<br />\n原文（法新社）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/erweiterung-der-antirassismus-strafnorm_copy-of-schweiz-hat-neuen-gesetzesartikel-gegen-homophobie/44595810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swissinfo.ch%2Feng%2Ferweiterung-der-antirassismus-strafnorm_copy-of-schweiz-hat-neuen-gesetzesartikel-gegen-homophobie%2F44595810&d=%2FsacCtyq6%2Fd%2BFgkrOoXRNr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7104d17b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/erweiterung-der-antirassismus-strafnorm_copy-of-schweiz-hat-neuen-gesetzesartikel-gegen-homophobie/44595810</a><br />\n<br />\n中文版<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/109763?fbclid=IwAR1NlLP1g-qwg5InVkYSNBki7PKN3NqX_pQ16rCNr3dmQ77EUzxcAF52RDE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F109763%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1NlLP1g-qwg5InVkYSNBki7PKN3NqX_pQ16rCNr3dmQ77EUzxcAF52RDE&d=%2FsacCtyq6%2Fd%2BFgkrOoXRNr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f63c9306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/109763?fbclid=IwAR1NlLP1g-qwg5InVkYSNBki7PKN3NqX_pQ16rCNr3dmQ77EUzxcAF52RDE</a>"},{"pid":"0d4cdc2c38493612f04c212c56b67f4eff52a316","tid":936960,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:42: